### **4. main_RealTimePlotMirror**  
**Description:**  
A live visualization tool that turns incoming numbers into a real-time line graph.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimePlotMirror - Live Data Charting Tool

RealTimePlotMirror renders real-time charts for metrics, sensors, or streaming numerical values.

## Features
- Matplotlib-powered scrolling chart  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Simple CLI integration  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_RealTimePlotMirror.git
cd main_RealTimePlotMirror
python visualize.py
